structured.name: Torsten Ludvig Valdemar Holmstrand
structured.description: Torsten Ludvig Valdemar Holmstrand was a Swedish manager born on July 20th, 1891 in Gothenburg. He studied at Y. Filip Holmqvist's institute in Gothenburg and was employed at Goteborgs Remfabr. A-B from 1907 to 1935. In 1917, he married Sigrid Larsson. He later served as a member and chairman of the board for Goteborgs Remfabr. A-B from 1936 onwards. He was awarded the Göta Goldinu Orden.
